---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Pricing - Treeline" description="Treeline is free. Here's what I'm thinking about for the future.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Treeline is free</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)] max-w-2xl">
        The desktop app, all plugins, CSV import, SQL access—everything. No account required, no subscription.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mt-4">
        Want automatic bank sync? <a href="https://www.simplefin.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">SimpleFIN</a> integration is available for $1.50/month, paid directly to them.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Why it's free -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        I built Treeline because I wanted a finance app that worked the way I think.
        Right now it's a passion project, and I'm sharing it because I think others
        might find it useful too.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <hr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)] mb-16" />

    <!-- Future thinking -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">What I'm thinking about</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        To keep Treeline sustainable long-term, I'm exploring some optional paid features.
        These aren't commitments—just ideas. I'd love to know what would actually be useful to you.
      </p>

      <!-- Feature cards -->
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Cloud backup</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">
            Automatic, encrypted backups so you never lose your data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Mobile app</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">
            Check your finances on the go. Sync across your phone and computer.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="feature-title">Partner reports</h3>
          <p class="feature-description">
            Automated email summaries to share with your spouse or partner.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Feedback CTA -->
    <section class="feedback-section">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What do you think?</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-6">
        I'd love to hear which of these would be useful to you—or if you have other ideas entirely.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://discord.gg/EcNvBnSft5"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="discord-link"
      >
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057 19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028 14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03zM8.02 15.33c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.956-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.956 2.418-2.157 2.418zm7.975 0c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.955-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.946 2.418-2.157 2.418z"/>
        </svg>
        Join the Discord
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="mt-16 text-center">
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-4">
        In the meantime, Treeline is ready to use today.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/download"
        class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-muted)] transition-colors"
      >
        Download for free
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .feature-description {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .feedback-section {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .discord-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    background: #5865F2;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: opacity 0.15s ease;
  }

  .discord-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    color: white;
  }
</style>
